			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1435573">
									

<p>This is neat, but&#8230; I can't help but feel like there should be more consensus on the org chart of the Foundation. Not to mention I would really like to see an org chart, rather than a flat list.</p>
<p>I'm not sure how I feel about the logos; you don't really see departments of the FBI, CIA, or other major organizations with their own unique logos, and I don't really see the Foundation having separate ones either. (Also, Gears likes to tell people that we don't really have a logo at all, so&#8230;)</p>
<p>I guess I'm just hesitant about this being labelled as a guide when it's really just one interpretation of Foundation structure.</p>

							</div>

								
					
