<p><a href="http://www.shutterstock.com/pic-70277599/stock-vector-snake-and-cup-caduceus-and-staff-of-asclepius-medical-symbols-each-image-on-it-s-own-layer.html">http://www.shutterstock.com/pic-70277599/stock-vector-snake-and-cup-caduceus-and-staff-of-asclepius-medical-symbols-each-image-on-it-s-own-layer.html</a></p>
<p>We're used to the one in the middle, though if we had our mythology right it should technically be the one on the right. What's the source of the snake and cup?</p>

